title: Beans & Greens Organic Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Little organic cafe opened Mar 2014 in Ipswich offering a range of vegetarian & vegan choices. Offers breakfast and lunch, fresh juices, smoothies, treats, and acai bowls. Almond, Bonsoy, coconut milk available for coffee drinks. Try the vegan nachos, raw pesto pizza, or raw zcchini pasta.
